%h1 ApiKey#new
%p
  Your current Api Key is
  %b= api_key.present? ? api_key : "blank"
- if api_key.blank?
  %p
    %small You will not be able to interact with MailChimp library unless you provider MailChimp API Key
- form_tag :api_key do
  %p
    = label_tag :api_key
    = text_field_tag :api_key
  %p
    = submit_tag 'Use this key'
  %p
    %small== We will not store your API key. It will be kept in Session. You can #{link_to 'destroy', destroy_api_key_path} it any time you want.